      • getConfigParametersControlsNode

        public Node getConfigParametersControlsNode()
                                     throws PortalException
        Returns the controls node for the configuration parameters.

        If no configuration parameters controls node was defined for this report type, a default one is generated and returned by this method.

        Returns:
        the configuration parameters controls node, or null if none was defined and a default could not be generated based on this report type.
        Throws:
        PortalException
        Since:
        4.2.0
